OL,3,CMum fears daughter's ME death could
OL,4,C'too easily' happen to someone else
OL,6,FAlso called chronic fatigue syndrome,
OL,7,FME is a long-term condition that can
OL,8,Faffect different parts of the body.
OL,9,FAccording to NHS England its cause is
OL,10,Funknown, but the most common symptom
OL,11,Fis extreme tiredness.
OL,13,FMaeve's mother, Sarah Boothby, gave
OL,14,Fevidence at an inquest into her death
OL,15,Fon Thursday 1 August. It follows
OL,16,Fevidence from doctors who saw Maeve in
OL,17,Fthe months before she died.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/17
