OL,3,CMum fears daughter's ME death could
OL,4,C'too easily' happen to someone else
OL,6,FOn Wednesday 31 July, Dr Thomas Fox
OL,7,Ftold the inquest he'd never seen an ME
OL,8,Fpatient with such severe symptoms as
OL,9,FMaeve.
OL,11,FMs Boothby said: "I'm hoping the
OL,12,Finquest will explain how she died. She
OL,13,Fwasn't expected to die, didn't want to
OL,14,Fdie.
OL,16,F"Death from ME is extremely rare -
OL,17,Fmalnutrition is common. I believe she
OL,18,Fdied from malnutrition and
OL,19,Fdehydration. I believe her death was
OL,20,Fpremature and highly preventable.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
