OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F435A1722589673
OL,3,CMum fears daughter's ME death could
OL,4,C'too easily' happen to someone else
OL,6,F"She had three separate omissions to
OL,7,Fthe Royal Devon and Exeter Hospital in
OL,8,F2021. It seemed to me the RDE didn't
OL,9,Frespond to the severity of her
OL,10,Fcondition and failed in its duty of
OL,11,Fcare.
OL,13,F"It did not take available specialist
OL,14,Fexpert advice on how to avoid
OL,15,Fmalnutrition and dehydration in ME."
OL,17,FMs Boothby told the inquest her
OL,18,Fdaughter had been a "healthy, robust
OL,19,Fchild" who started suffering from
OL,20,Fpersistent tiredness as a teenager,
OL,21,Feventually giving up PE at school.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/17
