OL,3,CMum fears daughter's ME death could
OL,4,C'too easily' happen to someone else
OL,6,FShe was eventually diagnosed with ME/
OL,7,FCFS at Frenchay Hospital in 2011 and
OL,8,Fher mother gave up her job to care for
OL,9,Fher, as a single parent, working part-
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,F"She couldn't cook, wash up, clean,
OL,13,Fget her benefits, make or attend
OL,14,Fappointments.
OL,16,F"We became socially isolated. In 2021
OL,17,Fshe couldn't sit up or hold a cup to
OL,18,Fher lip.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/17
