OL,3,CMum fears daughter's ME death could
OL,4,C'too easily' happen to someone else
OL,6,F"The hospital does not consider that
OL,7,FMaeve's death was preventable," he
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"It disagrees with the criticism that
OL,11,Fit failed its duty of care to Maeve or
OL,12,Fthat there were missed or important
OL,13,Fopportunities.
OL,15,F"At the time Miss Boothby made her
OL,16,Fstatement in March 2022, it was her
OL,17,Frecollection of what Dr Shenton had
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@_O]rD@AOUwD@AOU
