OL,3,CMum fears daughter's ME death could
OL,4,C'too easily' happen to someone else
OL,6,FMr O'Neill told the inquest how Maeve
OL,7,Fwould design and knit Harry Potter-
OL,8,Fthemed presents for her siblings every
OL,9,Fbirthday and Christmas.
OL,11,FHe added that his daughter "never
OL,12,Fwanted to die" but had hopes and
OL,13,Fdreams of what she might do in the
OL,14,Ffuture.
OL,16,FHe said: "She would have been better
OL,17,Foff in the hands of the NHS if she had
OL,18,Fcancer - I say this as someone living
OL,19,Fwith cancer. My treatment was swift,
OL,20,Fskillful and effective.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/17
